name: Bandz Rings
description:
These beauties are stackable finger rings. "Bandz" come in sets of 6. They can be worn as knuckle rings,  but can't be worn as close to the nail as the JBJ midis. Unlike the midis, these rings are closed in the back with no opening. Complete your armparty with a few "Bandz" today!

*Please view the demonstration photos*

name: Watch The Throne Studs
description:
I honestly believe these maybe my favorite studs at the moment.  These brass beauties

name: Linx Body Chain
description:

*Ladies upon ordering please leave me your waist measurement either in an email or in the notes section of the PayPal check out*

name: Custom Case DEPOSIT
description:
This listing is simply the DEPOSIT for a custom cell phone case.  Before paying the deposit I ask that you contact me with the following information:

● Cell Phone Model & Service Provider
● The color or colors you would like on your case
● The theme you'd like for your case to have (Hello Kitty, Chanel, or Mac for example)
 
Once I have this information I can quote you a price. After receiving your quote return to the website & proceed to pay the deposit fee. The deposit does go toward the total price of your case. I will not begin work on a case until the deposit payment has been received. If you choose  to cancel your order the deposit will not be refunded. It takes a week to order/receive the materials & 2 days to complete the case. 

**The photos are of my most recent cases**
